message:
My solution is to ask receiving host to send back an integer number to confirm the message has been received. Therefore on the server side:  
for (i=0; i<npass; i++){  
nbytes=send(fd, buf, size_buf, 0);  
..check nbytes here. nbytes=size_buf  
nbytes=recv(fd, &idone, 4, 0);  
..check nbytes. nbytes should be equal to 4   
}  

on the client size:  

 for (i=0; i<npass; i++){  
nbytes=recv(fd, buf, size_buf, 0);  
..check nbytes here. nbytes=size_buf  
nbytes=send(fd, &idone, 4, 0);  
..check nbytes. nbytes should be equal to 4   
}  

Juefu
